        <title>Medicare Home Health Flexibility Act of 2008</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Display Title</titleType>
        <title>Medicare Home Health Flexibility Act of 2008</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To ensure that home health agencies can assign the most appropriate skilled service to make the initial assessment visit for home health services for Medicare beneficiaries requiring rehabilitation therapy under a home health plan of care, based upon physician referral.</title>
      </item>
